                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6523" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0207</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9728 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">独立董事之困：康美案后何去何从？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Dilemma of Independent Directors: Where to Go After the Kangmei Pharmaceutical Lawsuit?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李胜楠，刘环宇，管兮，于剑乔，李子璇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">滨海能源发展有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">轻工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">独立董事权利；独立董事义务；强责任；独立董事制度；2022百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Independent directors rights; Independent directors obligations; Strong responsibility; Independent director system</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着广州市中级人民法院对康美药业一审判决落槌，其5名独立董事被判承担合计赔偿金额最高约3.69亿元的巨额连带赔偿责任，A股上市公司独立董事的“强责任”问题和独立董事制度再次得到理论界和实务界的广泛关注。本案例从康美药业判决后黎教授收到聘任其为独立董事的邀请展开，通过描写其顾虑重重的思考以及和其他两位独立董事的交谈和思维碰撞，全面回顾了康美药业财务舞弊案发过程及判决结果，从三位独立董事视角展现了他们任职过程中的作为、困惑与反思。本案例通过一手访谈资料，尝试引导学员了解中美独立董事制度差异，认识独立董事的权利与义务、履职障碍、履职风险及应对措施，同时启发学员从多个角度思考如何完善我国独立董事制度。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the first-instance judgment of Kangmei Pharmaceutical lawsuit by Guangdong Intermediate People&#39;s Court, five independent directors were sentenced to bear a huge amount of joint and several liability for compensation of up to 369 million yuan. The strong responsibility of A-share independent directors and the independent director system have once again received wide attention from theoretical and practical circles. This case starts from the fact that Professor Li received an invitation to appoint him as an independent director after the judgment of Kangmei Pharmaceutical. By describing his pondering and thinking collision in conversations with the other two independent directors, the case comprehensively reviews the process and judgment of financial fraud in Kangmei Pharmaceutical. In addition, the case also shows their actions, confusion, and reflection from the perspective of three independent directors. Through first-hand interviews, this case attempts to guide the students to understand the differences of independent director system between China and the United States, as well as the rights and obligations, the barriers and risks of duty performance and countermeasures. At the same time, inspire students to think about how to improve the independent director system in China from various perspectives.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公司治理模式；委托代理理论；声誉机制；信息不对称理论；独立董事的权利；独立董事的职责；独立董事的义务；独董制度的优化</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
